---

<section id="why" class="py-20 bg-white dark:bg-[#080808] border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-white/5">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-6xl">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4 uppercase tracking-tight">
        Value <span class="text-[#CC0000] italic">Kemitraan</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-white/60 text-lg max-w-3xl mx-auto font-light">
        Nikmati berbagai support eksklusif dan sistem yang telah terstandarisasi saat menjadi mitra franchise PITCAR.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 relative">
      <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-full h-full max-w-md bg-[#CC0000]/10 blur-[100px] rounded-full pointer-events-none"></div>
      
      <div class="group relative bg-slate-50 dark:bg-[#141414] p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-white/5 hover:border-[#CC0000]/40 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-[#CC0000]/10 hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300 overflow-hidden z-10">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-[#CC0000] scale-x-0 origin-left group-hover:scale-x-100 transition-transform duration-300"></div>
        <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-xl bg-[#CC0000]/10 flex items-center justify-center text-[#CC0000] text-3xl mb-6 group-hover:bg-[#CC0000] group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300">
          <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-slate-900 dark:text-white uppercase tracking-wide">Sistem Teruji</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-white/60 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Sistem operasional dan manajemen (ERP) terkomputerisasi yang terbukti optimalkan produktivitas outlet.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="group relative bg-slate-50 dark:bg-[#141414] p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-white/5 hover:border-[#CC0000]/40 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-[#CC0000]/10 hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300 overflow-hidden z-10">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-[#CC0000] scale-x-0 origin-left group-hover:scale-x-100 transition-transform duration-300"></div>
        <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-xl bg-[#CC0000]/10 flex items-center justify-center text-[#CC0000] text-3xl mb-6 group-hover:bg-[#CC0000] group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300">
          <i class="fas fa-hands-helping"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-slate-900 dark:text-white uppercase tracking-wide">Tim Auto-Pilot</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-white/60 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Staf ahli dan mekanik yang disuplai dan dipandu secara teknis oleh sistem sentral PITCAR.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="group relative bg-slate-50 dark:bg-[#141414] p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-white/5 hover:border-[#CC0000]/40 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-[#CC0000]/10 hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300 overflow-hidden z-10">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-[#CC0000] scale-x-0 origin-left group-hover:scale-x-100 transition-transform duration-300"></div>
        <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-xl bg-[#CC0000]/10 flex items-center justify-center text-[#CC0000] text-3xl mb-6 group-hover:bg-[#CC0000] group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300">
          <i class="fas fa-trademark"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-slate-900 dark:text-white uppercase tracking-wide">Branch Power</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-white/60 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Manfaatkan reputasi standar kualitas perawatan otomotif PITCAR yang sudah mapan.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="group relative bg-slate-50 dark:bg-[#141414] p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-white/5 hover:border-[#CC0000]/40 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-[#CC0000]/10 hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300 overflow-hidden z-10">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-[#CC0000] scale-x-0 origin-left group-hover:scale-x-100 transition-transform duration-300"></div>
        <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-xl bg-[#CC0000]/10 flex items-center justify-center text-[#CC0000] text-3xl mb-6 group-hover:bg-[#CC0000] group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300">
          <i class="fas fa-ad"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-slate-900 dark:text-white uppercase tracking-wide">Pusat Lead</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-white/60 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Distribusi lead customer lokal melalui dominasi digital marketing oleh tim pusat.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
